Licenses for incorporated software
==================================
Swift SHA2 Crypt contains some code derived from the following sources:

Passlib
-------
The source file ``Sha2Crypt/Sha2Crypt.swift`` contains code derived
from `Passlib <https://github.com/efficks/passlib>`_, a Python
implementation of password hashing library. It is available under
`BSD license <http://www.opensource.org/licenses/bsd-license.php>`_.
